# Components

## Folders
- `components/ui/` — reusable atomic primitives only
- `components/sections/` or `components/modules/` — large page blocks
- Page-specific pieces — subfolders under `components/`, not inline in `app/`

## Size & structure
- Split files past ~120 lines into smaller subcomponents
- Reusable pieces → `ui/`; page-specific pieces → named subfolders
- Follow existing patterns in `components/ui/button.tsx` and `badge.tsx` for cva + `cn`

## Custom vs library
- Trivial UI → build in `ui/` or `sections/` without new dependencies
- Complex third-party UI (shadcn, Magic UI, etc.) → use the `add-ui-library` skill
